.jumbotron
  %h1 The Art World in Your App
  .p
    The Artsy API provides open access to public domain works on <a href='http://artsy.net' target='_blank'>artsy.net</a> for educational and other non-commercial purposes. It's currently only available for playing, testing and learning only. Please <a href='mailto:support@artsy.net'>contact us</a> for all other inquiries.
  .p
    = link_to "Ready? Start Here", start_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg'
    = link_to 'Subscribe to the Dev Mailing List', 'http://groups.google.com/group/artsy-api-developers/subscribe', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg', id: 'subscribe_link'
  .p
    By using this API you agree to the <a href='/terms'>API Terms of Use</a>.

.alert.alert-danger
  Note that the API is in super early beta and is currently only available for testing, playing and learning. It's not yet suitable for production, has limited scope and will likely change.

.alert.alert-success
  Please do
  =link_to 'email us', 'mailto:engineering@artsy.net?subject=Artsy%20API%20Feedback'
  and tell us what you want to build or if you have any other feedback. We can't wait to see what you build!

